item.title: CVE-2019-10349|2024-08-04T22:17:20.334Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20dependency%20graph%20viewer%20plugin
item.description: A stored cross site scripting vulnerability in Jenkins Dependency Graph Viewer Plugin 0.13 and earlier allowed attackers able to configure jobs in Jenkins to inject arbitrary HTML and JavaScript in the plugin-provided web pages in Jenkins.
